      },
      {
        "q": "How many pairs of solutions do linear-quadratic simultaneous equations usually have?",
        "q_zh": "线性-二次联立方程组通常有多少组解？",
        "o": [
          "Exactly 1",
          "Up to 2",
          "Exactly 3",
          "Infinitely many"
        ],
        "a": 1,
        "e": "A line can intersect a curve at most at two points, so there are up to 2 pairs of $(x, y)$ solutions.",
