        "e": "The Cosine Rule ($a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$) can be rearranged to solve for the angle when all sides are known.",
        "e_zh": "余弦定理 ($a^2 = b^2 + c^2 - 2bc \\cos A$) 可以变形，在已知所有边的情况下求解角度。"
