  {
    "id": "kp-Y10.7-01",
    "section": "Y10.7",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Circle Theorems",
    "title_zh": "圆的几何定理",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "**Circle theorems** describe the geometric properties of angles and lines associated with circles.\n\n**Angle at the center** is twice the angle at the circumference standing on the same arc.\n\n**Angles in the same segment** are equal.\n\n**Angle in a semicircle** is always $90^\\circ$.\n\n**Cyclic quadrilaterals** have opposite angles that sum to $180^\\circ$.\n\n**Alternate segment theorem** states that the angle between a tangent and a chord is equal to the angle in the alternate segment.",
      "zh": "**圆的定理**描述了与圆相关的角和线的几何性质。\n\n**圆心角**等于同弧所对圆周角的两倍。\n\n**同弧所对的圆周角**相等。\n\n**直径所对的圆周角**始终为 $90^\\circ$。\n\n**圆内接四边形**的对角之和为 $180^\\circ$。\n\n**弦切角定理**规定，切线与弦之间的夹角等于该弦所对的圆周角（交错弧上的角）。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-circle-geom",
        "label": "Find missing angles in circles",
        "label_zh": "寻找圆中的缺失角",
        "description": "Calculate angles by applying one or more circle theorems, giving reasons.",
        "description_zh": "应用一个或多个圆定理计算角度，并给出理由。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-circle-geom",
        "question": "A, B, and C are points on a circle with center O. If angle $AOC = 130^\\circ$, find angle $ABC$.",
        "question_zh": "A, B, C 是圆心为 O 的圆上的点。如果角 $AOC = 130^\\circ$，求角 $ABC$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Identify the theorem. The angle at the center ($AOC$) is twice the angle at the circumference ($ABC$).\n\n**Step 2:** Calculate: Angle $ABC = 130^\\circ \\div 2 = 65^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $65^\\circ$ (Reason: Angle at center is twice angle at circumference)",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 识别定理。圆心角 ($AOC$) 是圆周角 ($ABC$) 的两倍。\n\n**步骤2：** 计算：角 $ABC = 130^\\circ \\div 2 = 65^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $65^\\circ$（理由：圆心角是圆周角的两倍）",
        "source": "Year 10 Assessment"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-circle-geom",
        "question": "ABCD is a cyclic quadrilateral. If angle $A = 85^\\circ$ and angle $B = 110^\\circ$, find angles $C$ and $D$.",
        "question_zh": "ABCD 是圆内接四边形。如果角 $A = 85^\\circ$，角 $B = 110^\\circ$，求角 $C$ 和角 $D$。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Use the theorem: opposite angles of a cyclic quadrilateral sum to $180^\\circ$.\n\n**Step 2:** Angle $C = 180^\\circ - 85^\\circ = 95^\\circ$.\n\n**Step 3:** Angle $D = 180^\\circ - 110^\\circ = 70^\\circ$.\n\n**Answer:** $C = 95^\\circ, D = 70^\\circ$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 使用定理：圆内接四边形的对角之和为 $180^\\circ$。\n\n**步骤2：** 角 $C = 180^\\circ - 85^\\circ = 95^\\circ$。\n\n**步骤3：** 角 $D = 180^\\circ - 110^\\circ = 70^\\circ$。\n\n**答案：** $C = 95^\\circ, D = 70^\\circ$",
        "source": "Adapted from Y10 curriculum"
      }
    ],
