  {
    "id": "kp-Y10.8-01",
    "section": "Y10.8",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Loci and Basic Constructions",
    "title_zh": "轨迹与基本作图",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "A **locus** (plural: loci) is a set of points that satisfy a specific rule.\n\n**Perpendicular bisector** is the locus of points equidistant from two fixed points. To construct it, draw two intersecting arcs of the same radius centered at the two points.\n\n**Angle bisector** is the locus of points equidistant from two intersecting lines. Construct it by drawing an arc across the lines and then two more arcs from those intersection points.\n\n**Locus at a distance $d$** from a point is a circle. From a line, it consists of two parallel lines.",
      "zh": "**轨迹**是满足特定规则的所有点的集合。\n\n**垂直平分线**是到两个定点距离相等的点的轨迹。作图方法：以两个定点为圆心，以相同半径画弧，使两弧相交，连接交点。\n\n**角平分线**是到两条相交直线距离相等的点的轨迹。作图方法：在角两边画一段弧，再从弧与边的交点出发画两段相交的弧。\n\n**到定点距离为 $d$ 的轨迹**是一个圆。到定直线距离为 $d$ 的轨迹是两条平行线。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-loci-regions",
        "label": "Shade regions satisfying multiple loci",
        "label_zh": "阴影表示满足多个轨迹条件的区域",
        "description": "Construct loci and shade the region that meets all inequalities (e.g., closer to A than B AND less than 5cm from C).",
        "description_zh": "作出轨迹并阴影表示满足所有不等式条件的区域（例如，离 A 比离 B 近，且离 C 小于 5cm）。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-loci-regions",
        "question": "Construct the perpendicular bisector of a line segment AB of length 6 cm.",
        "question_zh": "作长度为 6 cm 的线段 AB 的垂直平分线。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Set your compass to a width greater than half of 6 cm (e.g., 4 cm).\n\n**Step 2:** Place the point of the compass on A and draw arcs above and below the line.\n\n**Step 3:** Without changing the compass width, place the point on B and draw arcs that intersect the first two arcs.\n\n**Step 4:** Draw a straight line through the two intersection points.\n\n**Answer:** This line is the perpendicular bisector.",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 将圆规宽度设置为大于 6 cm 的一半（例如 4 cm）。\n\n**步骤2：** 将圆规针尖放在 A 点，在线段上方和下方画弧。\n\n**步骤3：** 在不改变圆规宽度的情况下，将针尖放在 B 点，画弧使之与前两段弧相交。\n\n**步骤4：** 过两个交点画一条直线。\n\n**答案：** 这条直线即为垂直平分线。",
        "source": "Year 10 Assessment"
