        "question_zh": "描述到定点 P 的距离恰好为 3 cm 的点的轨迹。",
        "solution": "The set of points at a constant distance from a fixed point forms a circle.\n\n**Answer:** A circle with center P and radius 3 cm.",
        "solution_zh": "到定点距离恒定的点集构成一个圆。\n\n**答案：** 以 P 为圆心，半径为 3 cm 的圆。",
