  {
    "id": "kp-Y10.9-01",
    "section": "Y10.9",
    "order": 1,
    "title": "Similarity in Area and Volume",
    "title_zh": "面积与体积的相似性",
    "explanation": {
      "en": "When two shapes are **mathematically similar**, their corresponding lengths are in the same ratio $k$ (the scale factor).\n\n**Area Scale Factor** is $k^2$. If the length increases by factor $k$, the area increases by $k^2$.\n\n**Volume Scale Factor** is $k^3$. If the length increases by factor $k$, the volume increases by $k^3$.\n\nThis principle applies to all similar 2D shapes and 3D solids, regardless of their complexity.",
      "zh": "当两个图形**数学相似**时，它们的对应长度之比为 $k$（比例因子）。\n\n**面积比例因子**为 $k^2$。如果长度增加 $k$ 倍，则面积增加 $k^2$ 倍。\n\n**体积比例因子**为 $k^3$。如果长度增加 $k$ 倍，则体积增加 $k^3$ 倍。\n\n无论其复杂程度如何，这一原理适用于所有相似的平面图形和立体图形。"
    },
    "examPatterns": [
      {
        "id": "ep-sim-av",
        "label": "Calculate area or volume of similar shapes",
        "label_zh": "计算相似图形的面积或体积",
        "description": "Use the length ratio to find missing areas or volumes, or vice-versa.",
        "description_zh": "利用长度比寻找缺失的面积或体积，反之亦然。"
      }
    ],
    "examples": [
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sim-av",
        "question": "Two similar triangles have corresponding sides of 4 cm and 12 cm. If the area of the smaller triangle is 10 cm$^2$, find the area of the larger triangle.",
        "question_zh": "两个相似三角形的对应边长分别为 4 cm 和 12 cm。如果较小三角形的面积为 10 cm$^2$，求较大三角形的面积。",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the length scale factor $k$. \n$k = 12 \\div 4 = 3$.\n\n**Step 2:** Find the area scale factor $k^2$. \n$k^2 = 3^2 = 9$.\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate the larger area.\n$Area = 10 \\times 9 = 90$ cm$^2$.\n\n**Answer:** $90$ cm$^2$",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 找到长度比例因子 $k$。\n$k = 12 \\div 4 = 3$。\n\n**步骤2：** 找到面积比例因子 $k^2$。\n$k^2 = 3^2 = 9$。\n\n**步骤3：** 计算较大图形的面积。\n$Area = 10 \\times 9 = 90$ cm$^2$。\n\n**答案：** $90$ cm$^2$",
        "source": "Year 10 Assessment"
      },
      {
        "patternId": "ep-sim-av",
        "question": "Two similar vases have volumes of 200 cm$^3$ and 1600 cm$^3$. If the smaller vase is 15 cm tall, how tall is the larger vase?",
        "question_zh": "两个相似花瓶的体积分别为 200 cm$^3$ 和 1600 cm$^3$。如果较小的花瓶高 15 cm，较大的花瓶有多高？",
        "solution": "**Step 1:** Find the volume scale factor $k^3$. \n$k^3 = 1600 \\div 200 = 8$.\n\n**Step 2:** Find the length scale factor $k$ by taking the cube root.\n$k = \\sqrt[3]{8} = 2$.\n\n**Step 3:** Calculate the height of the larger vase.\n$Height = 15 \\times 2 = 30$ cm.\n\n**Answer:** $30$ cm",
        "solution_zh": "**步骤1：** 找到体积比例因子 $k^3$。\n$k^3 = 1600 \\div 200 = 8$。\n\n**步骤2：** 通过开立方根找到长度比例因子 $k$。\n$k = \\sqrt[3]{8} = 2$。\n\n**步骤3：** 计算较大花瓶的高度。\n$Height = 15 \\times 2 = 30$ cm。\n\n**答案：** $30$ cm",
        "source": "Adapted from Y10 curriculum"
      }
    ],
