        "e_zh": "对于独立事件，将概率相乘：$0.4 \\times 0.5 = 0.2$。"
      },
      {
        "q": "In a tree diagram, what must the sum of probabilities on branches from a single point be?",
        "q_zh": "在树状图中，从单点出发的所有分支概率之和必须是多少？",
        "o": [
          "0.5",
